name: Deliverly Chaos
description:
Welcome to Deliver Chaos! A game where you have to deliver packages by throwing them into a truck and then driving to the destination! 

This is my first 'Game Jam' game, I don't expect it to be that good but it was fun doing this!

P.S 

I would recommed download the file because the browser game is kind of broken. Also level 1 is broken too. (Q to restart level)
